title: Pandan Chiffon Cake
description:
Ingredients:
6 egg yolks
100 g granulated sugar
150 ml vegetable oil 
140 ml coconut cream
200 g cake flour
1 1/2 tsp of pandan paste 
1 tsp of vanilla essence
2 tsp baking powder

For the meringue
9 egg whites
100 g granulated sugar
1 tsp of cream of tartar


If you can't find pandan paste go the traditional way
about 12 pcs  young, light green pandan leaves
rinse thoroughly and drain; chop roughly  then get about 5 tbs of water. Using a blender just blend the pandan and water . then strain it with a sieve and then squeeze the pandan juice use about 2 1/2 table spoon of pandan extract, if you want your pandan to be more vibrant green add a little bit of food coloring.
